blocks.subject: RE: ISDA
text: Would you like me to fax it to you?  If so, what is your fax no?

blocks.subject: RE: ISDA
text: As soon as I receive the document from Houston I will prepare a draft.

To answer your question, the ISDA will govern the transactions created by the parties.  There are various other terms and conditions on the website that govern issues such as privacy, the use of the website and the creation of transactions electronically.  If there are any particular provisions that cause you concern please let me know.
Tana I should be grateful if you could send the ISDA to me.

blocks.subject: ISDA
text: Thank you for your email dated 27th September, 2001 concerning ISDA
Agreement between Nordea (Merita Bank Plc) and Enron North America Corp.
With reference to your email we confirm that a copy of the ISDA Agreement
between Merita Bank Plc and Enron North America Corp. can be released to you
for the purposes of preparing an ISDA Agreement between Nordea (Merita Bank
Plc) and Enron Capital & Trade Recources Ltd..
Should you have any questions please do not hesitate to contact me.
P.S. We would appreciate if you could confirm that ISDA Agreement is
superiority to electronic trading agreement behind Enrononline trading
